Package controllers.appointment

Class AppointmentBaseController

java.lang.Object
controllers.BaseController
controllers.appointment.AppointmentBaseController
Direct Known Subclasses:
CreateAppointmentController, EditAppointmentController
public abstract class AppointmentBaseController extends BaseController
Base Appointment controller used for initializing UI elements that are shared between the Create Appointment Form and the Edit Appointment Form.
